<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3169] SaveIncremental does not work without signature</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3169</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I know this feature is ongoing, but with the 2.0.0-RC builds the saveIncremental (without signature) stop working at all. A ByteArrayOutputStream is used in the COSWriter for output. This OutputStream will only be handled in the case, when we write a signature. Otherwise the whole content will be discarded.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As I wrote some time ago on the mailinglist, incremental update work in a limited way. At the moment we use it for augmenting signatures and this works with the old 1.8.x but not with trunk after the patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1847&quot; title=&quot;TSA Time Signature&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1847&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1847&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was applied.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12922382">PDFBOX-3169</key>
